    <item>
      <title>美国市场转向 T+1 投资者面临 300 亿美元损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/investors-face-30-billion-cost-hit-as-us-markets-move-to-t-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国监管机构加快证券市场结算时间的计划将以全球投资者的代价为代价——根据 Bloomberg Intelligence 的最新报告，每年价值超过 300 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/investors-face-30-billion-cost-hit-as-us-markets-move-to-t-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
